3228917,Outliers: The Story of Success,0316017922,9780316017923,,B001ANYDAO,ATVPDKIKX0DER,US,https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1344266315l/3228917._SX98_.jpg,https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1344266315l/3228917._SX50_.jpg,2008,11,18,"Little, Brown and Company",eng,false,"In this stunning new book, Malcolm Gladwell takes us on an intellectual journey through the world of ""outliers""--the best and the brightest, the most famous and the most successful. He asks the question: what makes high-achievers different?

His answer is that we pay too much attention to what successful people are like, and too little attention to where they are from: that is, their culture, their family, their generation, and the idiosyncratic experiences of their upbringing. Along the way he explains the secrets of software billionaires, what it takes to be a great soccer player, why Asians are good at math, and what made the Beatles the greatest rock band.","{""id"":{""_"":""3364437"",""type"":""integer""},""books_count"":{""_"":""154"",""type"":""integer""},""best_book_id"":{""_"":""3228917"",""type"":""integer""},""reviews_count"":{""_"":""1093705"",""type"":""integer""},""ratings_sum"":{""_"":""2406368"",""type"":""integer""},""ratings_count"":{""_"":""577635"",""type"":""integer""},""text_reviews_count"":{""_"":""26322"",""type"":""integer""},""original_publication_year"":{""_"":""2008"",""type"":""integer""},""original_publication_month"":{""type"":""integer"",""nil"":""true""},""original_publication_day"":{""type"":""integer"",""nil"":""true""},""original_title"":""Outliers: The Story of Success"",""original_language_id"":{""type"":""integer"",""nil"":""true""},""media_type"":""book"",""rating_dist"":""5:242526|4:221795|3:87551|2:18142|1:7621|total:577635"",""desc_user_id"":{""_"":""1910836"",""type"":""integer""},""default_chaptering_book_id"":{""type"":""integer"",""nil"":""true""},""default_description_language_code"":{""nil"":""true""},""work_uri"":""kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.AiSrCsUeSMMsC_IUy2R8Cg""}",4.17,309,Hardcover,,545436,23962,https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3228917-outliers,https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3228917-outliers,"{""author"":{""id"":""1439"",""name"":""Malcolm Gladwell"",""role"":"""",""image_url"":{""_"":"" https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1564001739p5/1439.jpg "",""nophoto"":""false""},""small_image_url"":{""_"":"" https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1564001739p2/1439.jpg "",""nophoto"":""false""},""link"":""https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1439.Malcolm_Gladwell"",""average_rating"":""4.02"",""ratings_count"":""2194182"",""text_reviews_count"":""86267""}}","
